uctured and discoverable (29 tests in 2 files). Baseline generation deferred to next checklist item.\n\n## Iteration 31 — 2026-03-25T14:33:09Z — OK\n- **Log**: iteration-031.log\n\n","numLines":52,"startLine":550,"totalLines":601}}}
