r routes in default/disconnected state:\n- 12 tests covering: `/`, `/coinflip`, `/lord-of-rngs`, `/close-call`, `/close-call/abc123`, `/crash`, `/game-of-trades`, `/profile`, `/quests`, `/loot`, `/fairness`, `/leaderboard`, `/nonexistent` (404)\n\n**`states.spec.ts`** — Tests key UI state variants:\n- Connected/disconnected wallet states for home, coinflip, closecall, lord-of-rngs, referrals\n- Profile page with transaction history (empty state)\n- Error toast positioning\n- Lord-of-rngs tier selection and back-to-lobby flows\n\n### 6. **CI Configuration** (in `playwright.config.ts`)\n\n- `forbidOnly: !!process.env.CI` — blocks `.only()` in CI (prevents accidental test skipping)\n- `retries: 0` — no retry logic (visual tests should be deterministic)\n- `workers: 1` — sequential execution (parallelization not needed for visual)\n- Headless Chromium is the only project configured\n\n### 7. **Key Details**\n\n- **Gitignore**: Test artifacts (`test-results/`, `playwright-report/`, `playwright/.cache/`) are ignored; baselines in `__snapshots__/` are **committed**\n- **Determinism verification**: The fixture ensures two consecutive runs produce identical screenshots (zero-diff baseline comparisons)\n- **Diff detection**: Pixel diffs show in `test-results/` on failures; can be visually inspected\n- **Mock mode**: All visual tests run with `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"true\"` (no chain/wallet interaction)\n- **Viewport**: Fixed 1280×1080 (accommodates central container with `overflow: hidden`)\n\n### Files You May Need\n- **Main config**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts`\n- **Fixture**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n- **Spec**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/200-visual-regression/spec.md`\n- **History**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/200-visual-regression/history.md`"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: adf6dd851e83e485f (use SendMessage with to: 'adf6dd851e83e485f' to continue this agent